息丰富的来源”。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;N4E7jl&quot;>;Perplexity 发言人 Sara Platnick...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/3/24287157/perplexity -ai-election-voting-information-tracking-hub-us-presidential-election-2024-trump-harris&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/3/24287157/perplexity-ai-election-voting-information-tracking-hub-us-presidential-election-2024-trump-harris" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/3/24287157/perplexity-ai-election-voting-information-tracking-hub-us-presidential-election-2024-trump-harris</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-03T13:22:59-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-03T13:22:59-05:00</updated><title>任天堂的 Alarmo 可以运行《毁灭战士》吗？你打赌它可以</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;任天堂闹钟的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/31ZB1j1OrQ_nXDWW4wIIvvLUKdo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73697739/DSC_0955_2.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;这可是爆破恶魔。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;y7HHM9&quot;>;做什么&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/8/15/23306650/def- con-hacker-john-deere-tractors-run-doom-right-to-repair&quot;>;约翰迪尔拖拉机&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/6/14/ 22533512/doom-ikea-tradfri-smart-light-bulb-hack&quot;>;宜家智能灯泡&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/8/20/23308217/lego- rick-computer-james-brown&quot;>;乐高积木&lt;/a>;，以及&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/Circuitbreaker/2016/11/21/13697058/macbook-touchbar-doom-hack -sure-why-not&quot;>;MacBook Pro Touch Bar&lt;/a>; 有共同点吗？它们都可以运行《毁灭战士》，当然，任天堂的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24273422/nintendo-alarmo-review-alarm-clock&quot;>;可爱的 Alarmo 闹钟也可以时钟&lt;/a>;。有人实现这一点只是时间问题，但我没想到的是，当它实现时，它就可以玩了。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;4cfDYj&quot;>;这正是黑客 GaryOberNicht 所做的，他最近&lt;a 